# This content is from "advanced.md", line 21
msgctxt "chunk_3BF1A9B5"
msgid "#### Command Line Args\n"
msgstr "#### Argomenti della riga di comando\n"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 23
msgctxt "chunk_A2860DDF"
msgid "Execute the translation command in the command line to generate the translated document `example-mono.pdf` and the bilingual document `example-dual.pdf` in the current working directory. Use Google as the default translation service. More support translation services can find [HERE](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next/blob/main/docs/ADVANCED.md#services).\n"
msgstr "Esegui il comando di traduzione nella riga di comando per generare il documento tradotto `example-mono.pdf` e il documento bilingue `example-dual.pdf` nella directory di lavoro corrente. Utilizza Google come servizio di traduzione predefinito. Altri servizi di traduzione supportati possono essere trovati [QUI](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next/blob/main/docs/ADVANCED.md#services).\n"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 27
msgctxt "chunk_B3EB591F"
msgid "In the following table, we list all advanced options for reference:\n"
msgstr "Nella seguente tabella, elenchiamo tutte le opzioni avanzate per riferimento:\n"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 29
msgctxt "chunk_A2A42E6B"
msgid "##### Args\n"
msgstr "##### Argomenti\n"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 31
msgctxt "chunk_7A00EE21"
msgid "| Option                          | Function                                                                               | Example                                                                                                              |\n| ------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| `files`                         | Local PDF file path                                                                    | `pdf2zh ~/local.pdf`                                                                                                 |"
msgstr "| Opzione                          | Funzione                                                                               | Esempio                                                                                                              |\n| ------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| `files`                         | Percorso del file PDF locale                                                           | `pdf2zh ~/local.pdf`                                                                                                 |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 34
msgctxt "chunk_848B1EE1"
msgid "| `links`                         | Online files                                                                           | `pdf2zh http://arxiv.org/paper.pdf`                                                                                  |"
msgstr "| `links`                         | File online                                                                           | `pdf2zh http://arxiv.org/paper.pdf`                                                                                  |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 35
msgctxt "chunk_8B4991D7"
msgid "| `--output`                      | Output directory for files                                                             | `pdf2zh example.pdf --output /outputpath`                                                                            |"
msgstr "| `--output`                      | Directory di output per i file                                                             | `pdf2zh example.pdf --output /outputpath`                                                                            |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 36
msgctxt "chunk_D7ED91EE"
msgid "| `--<Services>`                  | Use [**specific service**](./Documentation-of-Translation-Services.md) for translation | `pdf2zh example.pdf --openai`<br>`pdf2zh example.pdf --deepseek`                                                     |"
msgstr "| `--<Services>`                  | Utilizza [**servizio specifico**](./Documentation-of-Translation-Services.md) per la traduzione | `pdf2zh example.pdf --openai`<br>`pdf2zh example.pdf --deepseek`                                                     |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 37
msgctxt "chunk_00AF4E48"
msgid "| `--help`, `-h`                  | Show help message and exit                                                             | `pdf2zh -h`                                                                                                          |"
msgstr "| `--help`, `-h`                  | Mostra il messaggio di aiuto ed esce                                                             | `pdf2zh -h`                                                                                                          |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 38
msgctxt "chunk_B0ABBFCE"
msgid "| `--config-file`                 | Path to the configuration file                                                         | `pdf2zh --config-file /path/to/config/config.toml`                                                                   |"
msgstr "| `--config-file`                 | Percorso del file di configurazione                                                         | `pdf2zh --config-file /path/to/config/config.toml`                                                                   |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 39
msgctxt "chunk_634BA748"
msgid "| `--report-interval`             | Progress report interval in seconds                                                    | `pdf2zh example.pdf --report-interval 5`                                                                             |"
msgstr "| `--report-interval`             | Intervallo di segnalazione dello stato di avanzamento in secondi                                                    | `pdf2zh example.pdf --report-interval 5`                                                                             |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 40
msgctxt "chunk_46037BF6"
msgid "| `--debug`                       | Use debug logging level                                                                | `pdf2zh example.pdf --debug`                                                                                         |"
msgstr "| `--debug`                       | Utilizza il livello di registrazione debug                                                                | `pdf2zh example.pdf --debug`                                                                                         |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 41
msgctxt "chunk_18BA0512"
msgid "| `--gui`                         | Interact with GUI                                                                      | `pdf2zh --gui`                                                                                                       |"
msgstr "| `--gui`                         | Interagisci con la GUI                                                                      | `pdf2zh --gui`                                                                                                       |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 42
msgctxt "chunk_0DA1F9CB"
msgid "| `--warmup`                      | Only download and verify required assets then exit                                     | `pdf2zh example.pdf --warmup`                                                                                        |"
msgstr "| `--warmup`                      | Scarica e verifica solo gli asset richiesti e poi esci                                     | `pdf2zh example.pdf --warmup`                                                                                        |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 43
msgctxt "chunk_D380BDDD"
msgid "| `--generate-offline-assets`     | Generate offline assets package in the specified directory                             | `pdf2zh example.pdf --generate-offline-assets /path`                                                                 |"
msgstr "| `--generate-offline-assets`     | Genera un pacchetto di risorse offline nella directory specificata                             | `pdf2zh example.pdf --generate-offline-assets /percorso`                                                                 |"

# This content is from "advanced.md", line 44
